{"type": "article", "id": 28483, "title": "奶昔包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-21T06:46:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162305bQ8fwOzJ7jvBgMTU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>奶昔要怎么喝才带感？俄罗斯设计师<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/RUSTAM_USMANOV\"> Rustam Usmanov</a> 给出的答案是：使劲摇呗。在这套名为 Shake my head 的奶昔包装上，你可以看到根据不同口味设计的人物造型，比如黑莓味的是绿皮肤的暴躁巨人、薄荷味的就是一个被冻住的骷髅。Usmanov 还为不同大小的杯型设计了每个人物的儿童版和少年版，为了让包装更有趣味，杯子两侧还有可以掀起的耳朵。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162302kAYZsH1I7NO9mUuJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.94754653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162303sURpiTa9PmcWDX3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57910448\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021623030hwPMoVacXmB5DuU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63455657\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162304tIOQxo4Zs7VeC21l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92394366\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}